title: R Markdown
text: You can include R Markdown files in your project.

title: R Markdown
text:
R Markdown
This is an R Markdown document. Markdown is a simple formatting syntax for authoring HTML, PDF, and MS Word documents. For more details on using R Markdown see http://rmarkdown.rstudio.com.
When you click the Knit button a document will be generated that includes both content as well as the output of any embedded R code chunks within the document. You can embed an R code chunk like this:

summary(cars)

     speed           dist       
 Min.   : 4.0   Min.   :  2.00  
 1st Qu.:12.0   1st Qu.: 26.00  
 Median :15.0   Median : 36.00  
 Mean   :15.4   Mean   : 42.98  
 3rd Qu.:19.0   3rd Qu.: 56.00  
 Max.   :25.0   Max.   :120.00

title: Open Science
text:
NMFS Open Science Resources
NMFS Open Science public home page
NMFS Open Science internal home page - Links to NMFS Open Science calendar of events
NMFS Open Science Resource Book
NMFS Openscapes is a collaboration between NOAA Fisheries and Openscapes to promote a data-driven culture through the adoption of open science tools and strategies. Openscapes provides team-based training in reproducible scientific workflows, data management, coding, and optimal team collaboration and project management. Keep an eye out for upcoming openscapes champions cohort opportunities on their webpage.
